In my opinion, one of the most valuable takeaways from any course of this kind is the network of people that you walk away with at the end. I learned a lot just from chatting with other S2DSers about what resources to look at for skills-building, what a data science job interview is like, and what it\'92s like to live in [insert country here]. I\'92m sure that many people will continue to help each other out in the search for data science jobs, and beyond.\
